Package: dyncomp
Type: Package
Title: Complexity of Short and Coarse-Grained Time Series
Version: 0.0.2-1
Author: Tim Kaiser
Maintainer: Tim Kaiser <Tim.Kaiser@sbg.ac.at>
Depends: zoo
Description: While there are many well-established measures for
        identifying critical fluctuations and phase transitions, these
        measures only work with many points of measurement and thus are
        unreliable when studying short and coarse-grained time series.
        This package provides a measure for complexity in a time series
        that does not rely on long time series (Kaiser (2017),
        <doi:10.17605/OSF.IO/GWTKX>).
